tool_description:
A non-official API for the Kings League InfoJobs. The data is hand collected and updated every week. It contains:

- List of teams with the info about each one (rank, league stats, etc.)
- List of players with the info about each one (team, position, league stats, oliver data, etc.)
- List of top scorers
- List of top assistants
title: Kings League Stats

api_list.name: Top assistants
api_list.description: Returns the list of top assistants for an specific season

required_parameters.name: seasonId
required_parameters.description: The season ID. Available season IDs: *2023-s1*

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://kings-league-stats.p.rapidapi.com/{seasonid}/top-assistants"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "kings-league-stats.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
